When importing issues from an existing system (like Redmine), it would be nice to be able to instruct the import script to add a link in the old system pointing to the new imported issue. 
This could be as simple as putting the link in a comment (with the name of the redmine user used by the JIRA import script). This way anybody landing on the old system could follow the breadcrumb to JIRA.

a use case for this would be when having a repository with many references to redmine tickets in its commit message log, so blaming some source file will show a mixture of redmine ticket numbers and JIRA issues numbers.

