As an AC addon, on receipt of a Webhook containing comment data, I want to be able to render that comment as it would be displayed in JIRA rather than in markup form.  

The current 2.0 expansions (below) do not end up rendering the comments, hence request.  Ideally would not want to have to either receive fully rendered content for ALL comments, when for the most part, only the most recent matters.
{quote}
https://jira.atlassian.com/rest/api/latest/issue/JRA-9?expand=names,renderedFields
{quote}

