h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Create a 'Select List' custom field;
# Add options with over 35 characters;
# Navigate to the Issue Navigator;
# Open the Simple Search mode;
# Click on 'More' to add the new Custom Field as a criteria;

h3. Expected Behavior
The option list would be displayed showing the entire name of the options - the box width would depend on the size of the longest string option.

h3. Actual Behavior
If options have the same initial name (e.g. "Client XXXXXXXXX - Operation XXX) users won't be able to differentiate one option from the other. If there are many options with the same name hovering all to find one is a painful process.

